{"id": 2209, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都是哪种追求美的类型？", "description": "在这个漫天都在高喊“看脸”的环境下，关于美这件事，你是怎么认为的？", "record_count": 16288, "comment_count": 23, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180305162252x5PVYnA8W71yN3zS.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-05T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3816, "title": "你都是哪种追求美的类型？", "content": "你是哪种追求美的类型？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 268453, "content": "贵在真实型，保持干净整洁就够了，keep real", "image": "img/option/option/20180305162359GTbmRtLgKeq2w93u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268454, "content": "运动健身型，把身体塑造得健康匀称，自律让我变美", "image": "img/option/option/20180305162420czly5qEt92g1VZid.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268455, "content": "人靠衣装型，衣服鞋袜包都是一个人时尚品味的体现", "image": "img/option/option/20180305162501Q63MA0PuUiR5thbK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268456, "content": "化妆修图型，不求奇迹变脸，但求精神饱满气色佳", "image": "img/option/option/20180305162524RWkwG7OjLxDldMrK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268457, "content": "内在性感型，与其装点生理门面，还是多看点书重要", "image": "img/option/option/20180305162605Sdagqp19XfO6hxsU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268458, "content": "技术微调型，割个双眼皮啥的现在也没啥大惊小怪的吧", "image": "img/option/option/20180305162627oXLmj0ErxIiKBwWS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268459, "content": "完全不care型，心里想想，该怎样还怎样", "image": "img/option/option/20180305162656YISyAhuGwTRZFLnB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268460, "content": "独辟蹊径型，自定义美，怎样才美我自己说了算", "image": "img/option/option/20180305162716mhzJAXkaPc0pN84Z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}